payload.text:
Yeh samasya "Silent Crash" (Chupchap Crash hona) ki wajah se ho rahi hai.

Browser (Chrome) aur Development mode mein React errors ko handle kar leta hai ya "Red Screen" dikha deta hai. Lekin App (APK/Production) mein agar koi choti si bhi JavaScript error aati hai, to poora React Tree freeze ho jata hai.

Isliye button dabne par koi action nahi hota, aur jab aap back jate hain, to purana error memory mein reh jata hai jisse baaki app bhi kaam karna band kar deta hai.

Main Problem Yahan Hai: Jab loading false ho jata hai, lekin questions array update hone mein kuch milliseconds le leta hai, tab currentQ undefined hota hai. Code currentQ.question_text_en padhne ki koshish karta hai aur App Crash ho jata hai.

Isse theek karne ke liye niche diya gaya Updated & Fixed Code use karein. Maine isme "Safety Checks" (Defensive Programming) add kiye hain.

✅ Fixed PYQSubjectiveScreen.tsx
TypeScript

import React, { useState, useEffect } from 'react';
import { ArrowLeft, ZoomIn, ZoomOut, CheckCircle } from 'lucide-react';
import { PYQQuestion, Language } from '../types';
import { api } from '../services/api';
import { useBackHandler } from '../hooks/useBackHandler';

interface PYQSubjectiveScreenProps {
  subject: string;
  year: number;
  onExit: () => void;
  defaultLanguage?: 'Hindi' | 'English';
}

export const PYQSubjectiveScreen: React.FC<PYQSubjectiveScreenProps> = ({ 
    subject, 
    year, 
    onExit,
    defaultLanguage = 'English' 
}) => {
  const [questions, setQuestions] = useState<PYQQuestion[]>([]);
  const [loading, setLoading] = useState(true);
  const [currentIndex, setCurrentIndex] = useState(0);
  // Default language ko prop se sync karein
  const [lang, setLang] = useState<Language>(defaultLanguage === 'Hindi' ? 'hi' : 'en');
  const [fontSize, setFontSize] = useState(16);

  // 1. Back Handler
  useBackHandler(() => {
    onExit(); 
    return true;
  });

  // 2. Data Fetching
  useEffect(() => {
    let isMounted = true; // Memory leak bachane ke liye

    const fetchQuestions = async () => {
        try {
            setLoading(true);
            const data = await api.getPYQs(subject, year, 'subjective');

            if (isMounted) {
                if (data && Array.isArray(data)) {
                    setQuestions(data);
                } else {
                    setQuestions([]);
                }
            }
        } catch (error) {
            console.error("Error fetching subjective questions:", error);
            if (isMounted) setQuestions([]);
        } finally {
            if (isMounted) setLoading(false);
        }
    };

    if (subject && year) {
        fetchQuestions();
    }

    return () => { isMounted = false; };
  }, [subject, year]);

  // 3. SAFETY CHECK: Agar loading nahi hai par questions khali hai
  const currentQ = questions && questions.length > 0 ? questions[currentIndex] : null;

  const handleNext = () => {
    if (currentIndex < questions.length - 1) {
      setCurrentIndex(prev => prev + 1);
    } else {
      onExit();
    }
  };

  const handlePrev = () => {
    if (currentIndex > 0) {
      setCurrentIndex(prev => prev - 1);
    }
  };

  // Helper for safe text
  const getTxt = (en?: string | null, hi?: string | null) => {
      if (!en && !hi) return "";
      return lang === 'hi' ? (hi || en || "") : (en || "");
  };

  // --- RENDER: LOADING ---
  if (loading) {
      return (
        <div className="h-[100dvh] w-full flex flex-col items-center justify-center bg-white dark:bg-slate-950 gap-4">
            <div className="w-10 h-10 border-4 border-brand-500 border-t-transparent rounded-full animate-spin"></div>
            <p className="text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 font-medium text-sm animate-pulse">Loading Questions...</p>
        </div>
      );
  }

  // --- RENDER: NO DATA ---
  if (!currentQ) {
    return (
      <div className="h-[100dvh] w-full flex flex-col items-center justify-center bg-white dark:bg-slate-950 p-6 text-center">
        <p className="text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 font-medium mb-4">
            No subjective questions found for {subject} {year}.
        </p>
        <button 
            onClick={onExit} 
            className="px-6 py-2 bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-800 rounded-lg text-sm font-bold text-slate-700 dark:text-white hover:bg-slate-200"
        >
            Go Back
        </button>
      </div>
    );
  }

  // --- RENDER: MAIN CONTENT ---
  return (
    <div className="h-[100dvh] w-full flex flex-col bg-white dark:bg-slate-950 font-sans text-slate-900 dark:text-white overflow-hidden">

      {/* HEADER */}
      <div className="px-4 py-3 pt-safe-header bg-white dark:bg-slate-950 border-b border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-800 flex justify-between items-center sticky top-0 z-50 shadow-sm">
        <div className="flex items-center gap-3">
          <button 
            onClick={onExit} 
            className="p-2 -ml-2 text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 hover:bg-slate-100 dark:hover:bg-slate-800 rounded-full"
          >
            <ArrowLeft size={22} />
          </button>
          <div>
            <h2 className="text-lg font-black text-slate-900 dark:text-white leading-none">Learn Subjective</h2>
            <p className="text-[10px] font-bold text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-500 uppercase mt-1">{subject} • {year}</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div className="flex items-center bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-900 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-800 p-1">
          <button 
            onClick={() => setFontSize(s => Math.max(12, s - 2))}
            className="p-1.5 text-slate-400 hover:text-brand-500 active:bg-slate-200 dark:active:bg-slate-800 rounded-md"
          >
            <ZoomOut size={16} />
          </button>
          <div className="w-[1px] h-4 bg-slate-200 dark:bg-slate-800 mx-1"></div>
          <button 
            onClick={() => setFontSize(s => Math.min(24, s + 2))}
            className="p-1.5 text-slate-400 hover:text-brand-500 active:bg-slate-200 dark:active:bg-slate-800 rounded-md"
          >
            <ZoomIn size={16} />
          </button>
        </div>
      </div>

      {/* PROGRESS BAR & LANG TOGGLE */}
      <div className="px-5 py-3 flex justify-between items-center bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 border-b border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-800 shrink-0">
        <div className="flex gap-1 overflow-x-auto hide-scrollbar max-w-[200px]">
            {questions.map((_, idx) => (
                <div 
                    key={idx} 
                    className={`h-1.5 rounded-full transition-all duration-300 shrink-0 ${idx === currentIndex ? 'w-6 bg-brand-500' : 'w-1.5 bg-slate-300 dark:bg-slate-700'}`}
                />
            ))}
        </div>
        <button 
            onClick={() => setLang(prev => prev === 'en' ? 'hi' : 'en')} 
            className="flex items-center gap-1 bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-800 px-3 py-1 rounded-full border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 text-[10px] font-bold text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300 shadow-sm shrink-0 active:scale-95 transition-transform"
        >
            {lang === 'en' ? 'ENG' : 'HIN'}
        </button>
      </div>

      {/* SCROLLABLE CONTENT AREA */}
      <div className="flex-1 overflow-y-auto p-6 pb-32 w-full bg-white dark:bg-slate-950">

        {/* Question Section */}
        <div className="mb-8">
            <div className="flex items-center justify-between mb-3">
                <span className="text-xs font-bold text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-widest">Question {currentIndex + 1}</span>
                {currentQ?.marks && (
                    <span className="bg-brand-50 dark:bg-brand-900/30 text-brand-600 dark:text-brand-400 px-2 py-1 rounded text-[10px] font-bold border border-brand-200 dark:border-brand-900/50">
                        +{currentQ.marks} Marks
                    </span>
                )}
            </div>

            {/* Optional Chaining (?.) ka use karein taaki crash na ho */}
            <h1 
                className="font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white leading-snug font-serif break-words select-text"
                style={{ fontSize: `${fontSize + 4}px` }}
            >
                {getTxt(currentQ?.question_text_en, currentQ?.question_text_hi)}
            </h1>
        </div>

        {/* Answer Section */}
        <div className="relative pl-4 border-l-2 border-green-500">
            <div className="absolute -left-[9px] -top-1 w-4 h-4 bg-green-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white ring-4 ring-white dark:ring-slate-950">
                <CheckCircle size={10} strokeWidth={3} />
            </div>
            <h3 className="text-green-600 dark:text-green-400 font-bold text-sm uppercase mb-3 ml-2">Solution</h3>
            <div 
                className="text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 leading-relaxed ml-2 font-serif break-words select-text"
                style={{ fontSize: `${fontSize}px` }}
            >
                {getTxt(currentQ?.answer_text_en, currentQ?.answer_text_hi) || 
                 getTxt(currentQ?.solution_short_en, currentQ?.solution_short_hi) || 
                 "Detailed answer not available."}
            </div>
        </div>

      </div>

      {/* BOTTOM NAVIGATION */}
      <div className="fixed bottom-0 w-full bg-white dark:bg-slate-950 border-t border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-800 p-4 pb-safe z-30 shadow-[0_-5px_20px_rgba(0,0,0,0.05)] flex gap-4">
        <button 
            onClick={handlePrev}
            disabled={currentIndex === 0}
            className="flex-1 py-3.5 rounded-xl font-bold text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-900 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-800 disabled:opacity-50 disabled:cursor-not-allowed active:bg-slate-200 dark:active:bg-slate-800"
        >
            Previous
        </button>
        <button 
            onClick={handleNext}
            className="flex-1 py-3.5 rounded-xl font-bold text-white bg-brand-600 shadow-lg shadow-brand-500/30 hover:bg-brand-500 active:scale-[0.98]"
        >
            {currentIndex === questions.length - 1 ? 'Finish' : 'Next'}
        </button>
      </div>

    </div>
  );
};
🛠️ Kya Changes kiye aur Kyun?
Safety Check (if (!currentQ)):

Maine ek block add kiya hai jo check karta hai ki currentQ exist karta hai ya nahi.

Agar questions array load ho gaya hai lekin empty hai, to purana code questions[0].something access karne ki koshish karta tha jo Crash kar deta tha. Ab ye "No Questions Found" screen dikhayega.

Optional Chaining (?.):

Maine har jagah currentQ.property ko currentQ?.property kar diya hai.

Iska matlab: Agar currentQ galti se bhi undefined hua, to app band nahi hoga, bas blank text dikhayega.

isMounted Check:

useEffect ke andar isMounted flag lagaya hai.

Kabhi-kabhi user screen se back kar deta hai jab data load ho raha hota hai. Purana code tab bhi state set karne ki koshish karta tha jisse "Memory Leak" aur freeze ho jata tha.

Language Toggle Fix:

Button click par setLang(prev => ...) pattern use kiya hai jo zyada reliable hai.

Main Div Fix (h-[100dvh] & overflow-hidden):

Mobile browsers/Webview mein scrolling issues theek karne ke liye height aur overflow properties ko fix kiya hai.

Is code ko replace karein, aapka App ab crash nahi hoga aur buttons smooth chalenge.  

subjective section app me kaam nahi kar raha hai vo yaha preview section me kaam karat hai par app deploy hone ke baad nahi karta subjectiove section pyq ka usem koi bhi butoom kaam nahi karta save and next bhi nahi kaam karta hai +- bhi kaam nahi karta hai hindi eglish toogle bhi kaam nahi karta hai aur uske baad back home screen pe aataa hon to vaja bhi kuhc kam nahi karta isse fix kro analayse karo pahle ki ais akyu ho rah hai aur phir fix karo upar le codes se inspiration lo agar vo helpfu;l hai to aur fix karo subjectiv escetion

